summary.summary: Inside; relatively cool weather. Outside; moderate and mild. Also, humidity should not be a concern and winds will be practically absent. A few light raindrops may fall, low clouds are expected, possibly some fog or persistent clouds, and it’s dark. The weather may change rapidly and become worse.
